title: S- on my level 6 taric
body: I finished a game with an S- on my level 6 Taric , Although I did not receive a level 7 mastery token do you get tokens for S- or do you only get them for S or S+  {{champion:44}} {{summoner:3}}

replies.body:
Yes for level 7 mastery you need 3 S's or S+'s

Once you get mastery 6, S- doesn't give you anything
